{"tid":856881,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先做到返工嘅日子都可以精神自然醒?","createTime":"2018-10-10T23:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T05:05:05.000Z","uid":21961,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1fea3fa6205c1ca7e3edc6ffadcfc62d7000973d","tid":856881,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:19:03.000Z","msg":"已經逼自己12點前訓<br />\n平時有做下運動<br />\n但係點解都唔可以好精神咁6/7點起身？<br />\n訓極都好攰好眼訓"},{"pid":"cf9bc574a6ea97e95f3e07b0869871d3f6476b07","tid":856881,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:45:01.000Z","msg":"慢性疲勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1bc180db2b4e1da7ef26ffd3d58ba908df0cc4","tid":856881,"uid":69168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:46:58.000Z","msg":"屌我相反，朝早一諗起要返工就札醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明放假可以訓到12點"},{"pid":"59939eaff95f631006c24285de0547247d9d5c2e","tid":856881,"uid":21961,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:49:51.000Z","msg":"最撚吹脹係<br />\n平時返工就要7點起身<br />\n唔洗返工都只係訓到9點幾<br />\n但我平時早訓兩個鐘又做唔到呢個效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係想每日精精神神咁起身"},{"pid":"fa7aed34d6c44fcec8262f86bf61fc9d2d9f0d5b","tid":856881,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:52:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c96ae7a8160df1e84a778780f1a827ebdea38e84","tid":856881,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:53:35.000Z","msg":"8點訓"},{"pid":"6be6b69a28579cb059639abb49eb0f76cdd92be2","tid":856881,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:55:25.000Z","msg":"唔好打丁 第日起身就精神啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日好撚眼瞓"},{"pid":"1639600a4abd083ad18eb905272f216f7cd7c7c4","tid":856881,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:01:11.000Z","msg":"7點起身 但5點幾已經扎醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674b563c188faef6b6f5502e222f0eec4ab61b91","tid":856881,"uid":204027,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:02:21.000Z","msg":"放假就會返工時間自然醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185f6089c9724b714f178c55387108da586cf213","tid":856881,"uid":81347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:02:22.000Z","msg":"之前返十點會自然醒"},{"pid":"26ddb098d2ea34c260c5a02e9dce730a4753b0f3","tid":856881,"uid":155558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:11:05.000Z","msg":"7點起身就最好11點前瞓，如果唔適應就慢慢每日早15分鐘校返正個瞓覺時間。<br />\n<br />\n另外你瞓覺有無鼻鼾聲？如果有，好大應會夜晚呼吸不暢順，不停醒下（無意識自己唔知醒過）又瞓返，供大腦嘅氧太少。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣朝早一起身無耐個人就開始想瞓，搭車又想瞓，返工返學都想瞓，食完午飯最想瞓，係十分辛苦，影響日常生活。"},{"pid":"4cec15a0547b92499f74fecc7bcdad63c18217d9","tid":856881,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ddb098d2ea34c260c5a02e9dce730a4753b0f3","tid":856881,"uid":155558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:11:05.000Z","msg":"7點起身就最好11點前瞓，如果唔適應就慢慢每日早15分鐘校返正個瞓覺時間。<br />\n<br />\n另外你瞓覺有無鼻鼾聲？如果有，好大應會夜晚呼吸不暢順，不停醒下（無意識自己唔知醒過）又瞓返，供大腦嘅氧太少。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣朝早一起身無耐個人就開始想瞓，搭車又想瞓，返工返學都想瞓，食完午飯最想瞓，係十分辛苦，影響日常生活。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"如果有鼻鼾係咪要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce5d6aacb3c50639c421b1901162d3a2bd32f43","tid":856881,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:37:29.000Z","msg":"11點好瞓啦，作息定時就會有精神"},{"pid":"d3f49eecfd658c2313cca3ecdf610c1cb9640995","tid":856881,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"你覺攰唔係因為唔夠瞓<br />\n係因為你唔想返工<br />\n思想上排斥依件事<br />\n換轉係放假朝早約咗女神睇戲 就唔會瞓極都攰"},{"pid":"a71ba6b9a14f41cdf2577aa4b1bbecf995681d86","tid":856881,"uid":166451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2